00:48:02,227 --> 00:48:04,362
Sayang, tidak pernah?

656
00:48:04,463 --> 00:48:07,299
Tidak pernah.

657
00:48:08,134 --> 00:48:11,003
Kevin, kau ini manis sekali.

658
00:48:17,144 --> 00:48:18,879
Baik.

659
00:48:36,628 --> 00:48:40,868
Satu, dua, tiga!

660
00:48:40,968 --> 00:48:42,969
Dia berhasil!

661
00:48:43,069 --> 00:48:49,441
Ric Flair baru saja mengalahkan
Juara Dunia Kelas Berat NWA, Harley Race.

662
00:48:49,541 --> 00:48:52,044
Di sana kau lihat, dia ada di layar,
Para pemirsa.

663
00:48:52,145 --> 00:48:54,013
Ric Flair, juara bar--

